OL,3,CBusiness fined after editing couple's
OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FA Jersey electrical company has been
OL,7,Ffined #4,000 and given a formal
OL,8,Freprimand by the data regulator after
OL,9,Fa "deliberate campaign to name and
OL,10,Fshame" a customer and his partner.
OL,12,FThis included animating their photos
OL,13,Fand attaching their faces to the
OL,14,Fbodies of rats in what the Authority
OL,15,Fcalls "a targeted and deliberate
OL,16,Fattack".
