OL,3,CBusiness fined after editing couple's
OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FIn November 2023, Jon Peacock, trading
OL,7,Fas Star-Delta Electrical Services,
OL,8,Fshared the couple's details on
OL,9,FFacebook during a payment dispute for
OL,10,Fwork carried out on the customer's
OL,11,Fproperty, an investigation by the
OL,12,FJersey Office of the Information
OL,13,FCommissioner has concluded.
OL,15,FThe Authority says the first public
OL,16,Fpost included the couple's names and
OL,17,Fphotos, as well as information about
OL,18,Fthe disagreement, and was shared more
OL,19,Fthan 800 times.
