OL,3,CBusiness fined after editing couple's
OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FIt explains that action led others to
OL,7,Fname the couple's employer, identify
OL,8,Ftheir home address and make insulting
OL,9,Fcomments such as calling them "scum"
OL,10,Fand "rats".
OL,12,FThe regulator adds that it informed
OL,13,FStar-Delta of a complaint and asked
OL,14,Ffor the original post to be removed
OL,15,Fwhilst enquiries were carried out, but
OL,16,Fthe company initially refused,
OL,17,Fclaiming it was not in control of the
OL,18,Fpage - although information from
OL,19,FFacebook's owner Meta later proved
OL,20,Fthat it was.
