OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FInstead, the Authority states that
OL,7,Fbetween December 2023 and February
OL,8,F2024, Mr Peacock shared more photos
OL,9,Fand videos of the couple on Facebook
OL,10,F"under the guise of low-level banter".
OL,12,FIt says many of these pictures were
OL,13,Fmanipulated and posted alongside their
OL,14,Fnames and insults.
OL,16,FThe couple told the regulator they had
OL,17,Freceived abusive and harassing
OL,18,Fmessages following the initial post,
OL,19,Fcausing them distress.
