OL,3,CBusiness fined after editing couple's
OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FThe regulator highlights that instead
OL,7,Fof taking the payment dispute to the
OL,8,FPetty Debts Court in the usual way,
OL,9,FStar-Delta chose to carry out this
OL,10,Fcampaign.
OL,12,FThe investigation also found that Star-
OL,13,FDelta was not registered with the
OL,14,FAuthority, which is illegal under data
OL,15,Fprotection law.
