OL,3,CBusiness fined after editing couple's
OL,4,Cfaces on rats in payment dispute
OL,6,FThe Authority says it offered the
OL,7,Fcompany the chance to respond to these
OL,8,Ffindings and the impact of the
OL,9,Fproposed fine on its finances, but
OL,10,FStar-Delta refused to give any
OL,11,Frelevant information.
OL,13,FThe regulator adds that Star-Delta had
OL,14,Fthe right to appeal but did not do so.
OL,16,FAlongside the fine and reprimand, Star-
OL,17,FDelta and Mr Peacock have been ordered
OL,18,Fnot to post about the couple on any
OL,19,Fsocial media platforms going forward.
