OL,6,FThe Authority concludes: "Information
OL,7,Fshould only be used for the purposes
OL,8,Ffor which it was given. It is not
OL,9,Facceptable to use that information to
OL,10,Fpublicly shame clients on Facebook as
OL,11,Fa means of prompting payment or
OL,12,Fotherwise settling a fee dispute."
